{"type": "article", "id": 6060, "title": "Tiki 沙发 & Bowl 小桌", "description": "", "date": "2015-02-10T07:47:26Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 7, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606143634BXzbEaCqZ1olIdOc.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t奥斯陆设计师 Andreas Engesvik 在今年的斯德哥尔摩家具展为瑞典家具品牌 Forgia ，带来了一款沙发 Tiki 与小桌 Bowl。Bowl Table 提供两种尺寸，使用一块薄薄的木皮层围合成一张碗形圆桌，搭在方形底座上，最底部由 4 根细腿支撑，在设计师看来，“碗型是一个极具美感和功能的载体，特别是在收集日常用品方面”。而 Tiki 则是一个看上去造型极致简单的沙发，柔软的线条与圆润的外形同样是靠 4 条细腿支撑。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143631Nu5fmtlQynzUrCRe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143632dkbWEGiUFJRu0y8C.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143632EQgDdCaf2F3weAkW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016060614363217XbiKBtnEZgU403.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71556122\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143633ElRSakJw196TCnYH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143633idBO3g6z2C9jxeZM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}